<li>Boiling point: 950 K ​(680 °C, ​1300 °F)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>History</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Naming: after France, homeland of the discoverer</li>
<li>Discovery &amp; First isolation: Marguerite Perey (1939)</li>
</ul>
